@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@newUsername = create_user_case_001

### 提示：正常创建会写入数据库；如需重复验证正常路径，请先修改 @newUsername 或重置种子数据

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：创建用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{newUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "real_name": "创建测试用户",
  "system_role": 2,
  "email": "create_user@example.com",
  "phone": "13800009999"
}

### 异常路径：重复用户名创建用户，预期 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{newUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "real_name": "创建测试用户",
  "system_role": 2,
  "email": "create_user@example.com",
  "phone": "13800009999"
}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录创建用户，预期 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "unauthorized_case",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "real_name": "未登录测试",
  "system_role": 3
}

### 异常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：普通员工创建用户，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "forbidden_case",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "real_name": "普通员工测试",
  "system_role": 3
}

### 异常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：缺少 username，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "real_name": "缺少用户名测试"
}

### 异常路径：system_role 不是整数，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "invalid_role_case",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "real_name": "角色类型错误测试",
  "system_role": "manager"
}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "username": "invalid_body_case",
    "password": "{{password}}",
    "real_name": "请求体错误测试"
  }
]
